des: Need real information? ...how to buy a home?, what closing costs mean to a buyer?, how to stage a home so it sells for more money?, de-clutering advice? what kind of market are we in now?, what is the STAR program and how do you apply? If you are looking to buy, sell or rent, you need a trusted advisor. This is not a multiple listing feed, this is real information that you need to have the least pain in a real estate transaction on Long Island. OR maybe you want to know about the Saint Patrick's Day Bar Crawl or the best places to see the Fourth of July fireworks, or the newest village restaurant... the information changes frequently so you can always find the information posted here on my BLOG www.northshorelongislandhomes.wordpress.com I am here to help, just ask ALEXA for your "long Island Real Estate update".
